{
  "id": "adv_card_mhk_03_01_short",
  "title": "miho 1話  もうひとりの優勝者 (Short)",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "3d_toffice_evening",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "（NEXT VENUSグランプリ、歴代の優勝者を）\n（一堂に集めて祭典が行われることになった）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（The Next Venus Grand Prix‚ gathering all the past champions.）\n（It's become a festival where they all come together.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "（星見プロからは、月ストとサニピが出演する）\n（……そして、うちの優勝経験者といえばもう一人……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（From Hoshimi Pro‚ Moon Tempest and Sunny Peace will perform.）\n（And… there's another former winner from our agency…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11.5666666348,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_01-mhk001.m4a",
      "text": "お断りします",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'll decline.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 16.4999994595,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "いや、話くらい最後まで聞いて下さいよ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ please listen to the end of the story…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 18.2666673978,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "mihoさんもスリクスを結成する前に……\nSundanceとしてグランプリで優勝してますよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Before forming IIIX‚ miho-san…\nYou won the Grand Prix as Sundance‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 24.3666673978,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_01-mhk002.m4a",
      "text": "……私の前のグループをご存じだったんですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…So you knew about my previous group.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 27.9000020027,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "そりゃ知ってますよ。俺はマネージャーですよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Of course‚ I knew it. I'm the manager.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 31.3333362262,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "（Sundanceは、藤代葉さんとの二人組で）\n（BIG4にも迫ろうかという人気ユニットだった）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Sundance‚ a duo with Fujishiro You before IIIX‚）\n（they were a popular unit approaching the BIG4.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.633338515,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "（しかし人気絶頂期に活動休止）\n（その後、mihoさんはⅢXを結成したわけだが……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（But they went on hiatus at the height of their popularity.）\n（After that‚ miho-san formed IIIX…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.4000036557,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_01-mhk003.m4a",
      "text": "……昔のことですよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…That's all in the past.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 49.9666693051,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "どうでしょう、先方もmihoさんに\nぜひ出てほしいとおっしゃってますし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What do you think? They really want miho-san\nto participate‚ you know.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 54.6000036556,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_01-mhk004.m4a",
      "text": "お断りします\n今、スリクスは新曲リリースの準備で忙しいんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'll decline.\nRight now‚ IIIX is busy preparing for a new song release.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 58.6666749,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}